{
  "stem": "8252.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, as you'll find out, we already had some ways of getting our own food and so on, but that was in different camps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In this camp, the work was pretty hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although, at the very beginning, we went to do some work in agriculture, in farms and so on, and I remember trying to get some hay on a fork.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, this kid who was playing in nightclubs and so on, never worked with his hands, and that wasn't very easy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to learn that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to learn to work physically.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what happened was that I was one of the hardest workers because, if you finished this kind of work up to this point, if you get to this point in your work, digging a ditch, for example, you can sit down, and that's your day.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the Germans would assign you certain amount of work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was-- that was pretty hard to-- to get into that kind of work, especially that I was with a group of Polish peasants.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because who was pulled into the army were Polish peasants who went to-- to do agriculture work in France.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These were the-- these were the friends that I had-- that I fought with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, they-- to them, this kind of physical work was-- was nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To me, it was-- believe me, it was something at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the first day when I couldn't get the hay on my fork, so they sent me up into the barn to just walk on hay, to-- to-- to make it-- you know, to pat it down.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was my work for the day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Pretty tiring, but, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
